Full Description: Côtes de Femme, translates “Sides of Woman” representing the many beautiful shapes, curves, tones, and types of women.  Côtes de Femme also represents the mystère of a woman, the infinite facets of her being…a powerful creature that cannot be tamed, or truly understood, but respected, cherished, and loved. As a longtime dream for Kristin and I, we founded the Côtes de Femme wine brand from our hearts, our love story, and from our love of others. We created a Lifestyle brand whereby our community are just people like us, who want to fee empowered, loved, lifted, and be better prepared to take on the day tomorrow. We launched our wine brand in January of 2020 with our Côtes de Provence Rosé. Later that year, we brought to market our award-winning Alexander Valley Cabernet Sauvignon.  What makes our wine even more special than the quality in the bottle is our one-of-a-kind packaging. Every bottle comes with our patented rhinestone bracelet that decorates the neck of the bottle which can be removed to decorate your stemware. Our packaging continues to help our wine fly off the shelves and be a hit poolside or at the beach! We look forward to our continual growth in this super competitive industry. We continue to be amazed by the new relationships that we get to create. Relationships that really become lifelong friendships and family. We are amazed at the investment that others are putting in us. These investments show us that we really have something special here, a deep community of people who want to love life and "Live Extra"!!!
